Use the standard library
This is how to sum_product of numbers:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that prod is 1
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this numbers's length times:
      Remember that total is sum of total and (item i in numbers)
      Remember that prod is product of prod and (item i in numbers)
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is [total, prod]
Now you know

>>> sum_product of []
[0, 1]
>>> sum_product of [1, 2, 3, 4]
[10, 24]
>>> sum_product of []
[0, 1]